original_title: Richmond: Sharrott Avenue - Pleasant Plains Boulevard
text:
119 Sharrott Avenue, east side, south of Pleasant Plains Boulevard, showing the old Manee House (as stated by P. L. Sperr). The maps from 1853 to 1918 show it to have been on the A. Latourette property.

August 27, 1930

P. L. Sperr
